sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as 📱 Player (Flutter)
    participant A as 🅰️ Admin (Angular)
    participant API as 🍃 Spring Boot
    participant SEC as 🔐 JWT Filter
    participant DB as 🍃 MongoDB

    Note over P,DB: ── AUTH FLOW ──

    P->>API: POST /api/auth/login { email, password }
    API->>DB: findUserByEmail()
    DB-->>API: User document
    API->>API: BCrypt verify password
    API->>API: Generate JWT (role: PLAYER)
    API-->>P: { token, role, userId }

    Note over A,DB: ── ADMIN LOGIN ──

    A->>API: POST /api/auth/login { email, password }
    API->>DB: findUserByEmail()
    DB-->>API: User (role: ADMIN)
    API-->>A: { token, role: ADMIN }

    Note over A,DB: ── ADMIN CREATES PUZZLE + CLUES ──

    A->>SEC: POST /api/admin/puzzles [Bearer ADMIN JWT]
    SEC->>SEC: Validate JWT + check ADMIN role
    SEC->>API: Forward request
    API->>DB: insert puzzle document
    DB-->>API: saved puzzle { id }
    API-->>A: 201 Created { puzzleId }

    A->>SEC: POST /api/admin/puzzles/{id}/clues
    SEC->>API: Forward (ADMIN validated)
    API->>DB: insert clue linked to puzzleId
    DB-->>API: saved clue
    API-->>A: 201 Created { clueId }

    Note over P,DB: ── PLAYER GAME FLOW ──

    P->>SEC: GET /api/puzzles [Bearer PLAYER JWT]
    SEC->>API: Forward (PLAYER validated)
    API->>DB: findAllActivePuzzles()
    DB-->>API: puzzles[]
    API-->>P: puzzles list

    P->>SEC: POST /api/game/start { puzzleId }
    SEC->>API: Forward
    API->>DB: create GameProgress { userId, puzzleId, clueIndex:0 }
    DB-->>API: progress saved
    API->>DB: getClue(puzzleId, index: 0)
    DB-->>API: first clue
    API-->>P: { clue, hint, type }

    P->>SEC: POST /api/game/answer { progressId, answer }
    SEC->>API: Forward
    API->>DB: getProgress(progressId)
    DB-->>API: GameProgress
    API->>API: validate answer (case-insensitive)
    API->>DB: update progress clueIndex++
    API->>DB: getNextClue()
    DB-->>API: next clue
    API-->>P: { correct: true, nextClue }

    Note over P,DB: ── PUZZLE COMPLETE ──

    P->>SEC: POST /api/game/answer (final answer)
    API->>DB: mark progress COMPLETED
    API-->>P: { complete: true, score, timeTaken }
